WinDom installation
-------------------

Just unpack the current archive and copy files from 'include' and 
'lib\compiler' of WinDom package in your compiler include and lib 
directory.

WinDom is available for GCC 2.95+, but it should be compiled for
Pure C, Sozobon C, and Gcc 2.8.1 as well.

windom2 requires GEMLIB 0.43.5+ and LDG-DEV packages:

GEMLIB:
http://arnaud.bercegeay.free.fr/gemlib/ 

LDG-DEV:
http://ldg.sf.net
